  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK1015">
<l>piṟarpaḻiyun tampaḻipō ṉāṇuvār nāṇuk </l>
<l>kuṟaipati yeṉṉu mulaku</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The world regards as the abode of modesty him who fear his own and other's guilt.</l>
            </lg>
